criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Maxillofacial bone defect patients between 16 to 60 years old, without gender limit;
2. The maxillofacial bone defect should be caused by severe periodontitis, cleft lip and palate or alveolar cleft;
3. No systemic disease;
4. No unhealthy living habit;
5. The patients must be informed and agreed with this experiment with signing Informed consent form.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Patient has participated in other clinical experiment in four weeks before the initiation of our experiment; 
2. Using or once long term used bisphosphonates;
3. Using aspirin in nearly 5 days;
4. Pregnant or lactating women;
5. Failed to meet the age requirement;
6. Systemic disease or abnormal renal and liver function.
